{"tid":1043761,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)死神又又又來了","createTime":"2019-03-02T13:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T21:01:53.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e75a22b58cb89dcfd3ed2934f8cf067dfef7dd9","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=dcb92965\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=4a8664fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=27bd7f61\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/18/Final_Destination_5_teaser_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F18%2FFinal_Destination_5_teaser_poster.jpg&h=9789f75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.此集除了上述提到大規模斷橋意外，有眼睛雷射手術意外，更有體操選手因摔出去而多處骨折的恐怖畫面，讓觀眾感受無法直視的恐懼；還有針灸治療意外，一名整個正面及臉部被插滿針的病患，以正面跌落在地，針全部扎進身體等等的意外，都讓大家坐立難安，無法承受下一刻即將發生狀況&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.故事講述一批來自MT. Abraham高中40名師生乘180航班到巴黎參加畢業旅行。在飛機起飛前，其中一位男學生Alex預見飛機會發生意外，機上無一生還，其後他跟另外5名學生和1名女教師被趕下機，結果飛機起飛不久真的出了意外，全部乘客罹難，而這當初被趕下機的7人會在意外以後接二連三地順著次序死去.....<br />\n<br />\n3.女主角Kimberly Corman在高速公路開車時，突然出現預感。她預見到23號公路第180哩，即將發生的連環大車禍，她和周圍的很多人死於車禍中。之後Kimberly決定立刻改變方向，堵住高速公路的路口隨即，連環車禍真的發生了，只不過因為她的堵住了路口，使她和一些本身要在車禍喪生的人幸免於難。可是與Kimberly同行的三位同學：Shaina McKlank、Dano Estevez和Frankie Whitman仍然被一輛拖車撞死<br />\n<br />\n4.於「180航班墜機事故」發生後的5年[3]，主角Wendy Christensen與她的同學們坐雲霄飛車「惡魔航班」時，她突然出現預感，於預感中坐「惡魔航班」的人將全部死去。後來Wendy於預感中回神過來後，她喊叫要求離開「惡魔航班」，因而引起其中一名同學Lewis Romero的不滿，大罵Wendy的所作所為非常幼稚，而Wendy的朋友Kevin Fischer為了替Wendy出頭，與Lewis發生爭執，引起混亂，使部分乘客被迫離開了「惡魔航班」。但是仍有很多人不相信她的話...<br />\n<br />\n5.180號班機墜機事件的10年後。一個預知到賽車意外即將發生的青少年Nick（包柏&middot;坎比飾）。他警告他的朋友關於預測的災難預告，他的朋友全都因而逃過這場意外災難大難不死後卻發現死神回來，一一解決本來應該死卻沒死的人..<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=39686469\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=8f511ed4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fe6a26840dbef6fdb557bc1d03ce4326badef5","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7800846352c39450943fee5c0ccd7228dca36ac1","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2388615e3d1b624a0aab1e99cb90805ecef5eb10","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c37f8962103e132110459a2191a0c774114e71","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16651fb10883efea0c2eaa20d58260d620f6ba47","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71aae5b58164e9be3f185077922b1c124e7a1cef","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T19:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c337f307949453d1f802f66f8e09787555475761","tid":1043761,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T21:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}